'''Cadet commander''' was a rank given to the foremost [[Cadet/Legends|cadet]] at the [[Syndic Mitth'raw'nuruodo training academy]], who served as a leader of the other cadets. [[Shawnkyr Nuruodo]] held this rank in [[19 ABY/Legends|19 ABY]] before turning it over to [[Jagged Fel]] when Fel helped defeat a [[Pirate/Legends|pirate]] raid.

